## <img class="logo" src="/sublime.svg" /> Sublime Text

<a href="/resources/sublime.png"><img src="/resources/sublime.png" /></a>

The [sublime-eno](https://packagecontrol.io/packages/eno) package offers syntax
highlighting for eno with a light and dark theme.

Visit [sublime-eno](https://packagecontrol.io/packages/eno) package on packagecontrol.io.
